---
title: "transferForSwap (FeeAggregator)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_access: require whenNotPaused, SWAPPER_ROLE
    q_check_access --> q_check_empty: access granted
    q_check_empty --> q_revert_empty: assetAmounts.length == 0
    q_revert_empty --> [*]: revert EmptyList
    q_check_empty --> q_loop: not empty
    q_loop --> q_check_asset: i < assetAmounts.length
    q_loop --> [*]: i >= assetAmounts.length
    q_check_asset --> q_revert_not_allowed: NOT s_allowlistedAssets.contains(asset)
    q_revert_not_allowed --> [*]: revert AssetNotAllowlisted
    q_check_asset --> q_transfer: asset is allowlisted
    q_transfer --> q_loop: _transferAsset(to, asset, amount), emit AssetTransferredForSwap

    note right of q_check_asset
        INV-001: Only allowlisted assets can be transferred for swap
        INV-002: Only SWAPPER_ROLE can initiate transfers (auction contract)
        INV-003: FeeAggregator is the custody point for protocol revenue tokens
    end note
